{
  "stem": "1860.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 289.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My husband will tell you more-- more about it because he-- he remembers it very distinctly.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then at March '43, I think so, the director of the enamelware factory, Schindler, decided to-- to create a sub camp in-- on the premises of Emalia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he built barracks and he detained all his workers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from then on, we lived there on premises, and we worked there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we did not have to go anymore to Plaszow and that was a tremendous relief.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- we sort of felt protected by Schindler.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were not-- not afraid of shootings, and selections, and so on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew we have to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- we were relatively safe for the time being, that Schindler won't let anything bad happen to us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two levels, the lower and upper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a like a communal stove in the-- in the center of the barrack.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And yes, they were-- not a question how different they were, but we had a little bit of peace of mind.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew that if Schindler is with us he-- he will protect us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We somehow trusted the man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- we-- we believed that-- that he will do whatever is in his power to-- to help us, to pull us through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, one could-- when one had a boyfriend, one had a brother, or a husband, and one would approach Schindler, listen, could-- could you arrange that he could come to the factory and work.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he-- he-- if he could, he obliged.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when we had some-- I don't mean we-- I, personally, but people had some valuables, diamonds, and we were giving it to Schindler.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he also needed a lot of valuables to-- to bribe the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
